This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to improve narrative comprehension. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with improving the performance of the model, which falls under cs.LG (Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the integration of structured commonsense knowledge, which falls under cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
